_sText: Here is my latest deagle5 map, gg_deagle5_power. I started off a loose design of a power station for a mod, but I ended up turning it into a deagle5 map. I think it turned out really well for me being sick when I made it and I hope you enjoy it as well. The box texture is custom, and the detail bump makes it look amazing. Thank you deathangel for making the custom studio logo Thank you hacksawjack for making the nosoul inc logo. All textures are included in the BSP, so no extra downloading is required.
